{[%evp 0,14,20,12,29,4,18,19,26,27,27,26,41,41,44,44,36] In this Line we
encounter 4 Different pawn Structures.} 1. d4 Nf6 2. Bg5 Ne4 3. Bf4 c5 4. d5 e6
(4... d6 5. f3 Nf6 6. e4 g6 {[%emt 0:00:03] Structure 3.}) (4... Qb6 5. Nd2
Qxb2 {or} (5... Nxd2 6. Bxd2 Qxb2 {[%emt 0:00:04] Both lead to Structure 4.}))
5. f3 Nf6 6. e4 (6. Nc3 exd5 7. Nxd5 Nxd5 8. Qxd5 {[%emt 0:00:02] Structure 2.}
) 6... exd5 7. exd5 d6 {[%emt 0:00:01] Structure 1.} *

