1. d4 Nf6 2. Bg5 Ne4 3. Bf4 c5 4. f3 Nf6 5. d5 e6 6. Nc3 exd5 7. Nxd5 Nxd5 8.
Qxd5 Qf6 $6 9. Be5 Qe6 10. O-O-O {[%cal Gd1d5] White insists on recapturing on
