White is fighting for equality already.} 8. a3 Be7 $1 {There is no need to
exchange our strong bishop.} 9. f4 c5 {It is very hard for White to keep his
centre intact without the dark-squared bishop.} 10. dxc5 (10. Nf3 $6 a6 11. Ne2
Nc6 12. c3 Bd7 {I believe that Black should be more than happy with his
position. White's pieces look silly.}) 10... Bxc5 11. Nf3 Nc6 12. Bd3 (12. h4 {
