{[#] This structure arises after 1.d4 Nf6 2.Bg5 e6 3.e4 h6 4.Bxf6 Qxf6 5.c3 d5.
Having a bishop pair, Black wants to obtain a French type of structure. In the
next fragment, I explain why it's better to keep the tension with 6.Bd3.}  *

